### MongoDB Pagination Endpoints Overview
# This file provides an overview of all MongoDB pagination endpoints

# --- Variables ---
@host = http://localhost:8000
@api_key = your_api_key_here
@auth_token = Bearer {{api_key}}

# ===========================================
# PAGINATION PATTERN
# ===========================================
# All endpoints follow the same pagination pattern:
# - page: Page number starting from 1
# - limit: Hardcoded to 10 items per page
# - offset: Calculated as (page - 1) * 10
# 
# Response format:
# {
#   "items": [...],
#   "page": 1,
#   "limit": 10,
#   "total": 100,
#   "has_more": true
# }

# ===========================================
# QUOTES ENDPOINTS
# ===========================================
# Base URL: /api/v1/mongo/quotes/

### Recent Quotes
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/recent?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Oldest Quotes
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/oldest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Highest Value Quotes
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/highest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Lowest Value Quotes
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/quotes/lowest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

